## 3. Evidence Reliability Guidance

| Evidence Type | Reliability | Analyst Note |
|---|---|---|
| Raw SIEM / NetWitness logs | High | Validate timestamp, parser quality, and source integrity. |
| Endpoint telemetry | High | Validate process tree, file artefacts, persistence, and user context. |
| Network telemetry | High | Validate direction, destination, protocol, and whether traffic succeeded. |
| Threat intelligence | Medium | Treat as context until supported by local telemetry. |
| Analyst notes | Medium | Useful for reasoning, but should reference technical evidence. |

